{"tid":1499433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中国有文革復辟的勢頭, 香港是新黑5類, 是高危人種之一","createTime":"2019-08-23T17:02:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:22:54.000Z","uid":76310,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"0ed039cf00417a8364985b10fffc16098b7f595e","tid":1499433,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:02:47.000Z","msg":"中国有文革復辟的勢頭, 香港是新黑5類, 是高危人種之一<br />\n<br />\n中国現在不斷鼓動極端民族主義<br />\n中国要將中国国內的不滿情勢指向其他地方, 而不是對向政權<br />\n很難理解嗎? <br />\n清朝末年, 很多人反清朝, 口號是: 反清復明, 結果清政府將不滿情緒向外, 變成扶清滅洋<br />\n現在中国要將愛国主義+民眾不滿情緒向外, 新黑5類會是高危類別<br />\n不論你是藍絲或黃絲, 都是中国利用給群眾發洩的對象<br />\n台灣, 香港, 新疆, 西藏, 還有一類忘記了是什麼<br />\n<br />\n真心說, 只要你是香港人, 就算你沒有去示威或者遊行, 總之香港人就是高危類別<br />\n你們勸身邊的人, 只要是香港人, 就很高危"},{"pid":"b8c26e3403ceab0012514671f59bc62704641904","tid":1499433,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:07:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27869f95b94d98e83fc9878b167f3d34b61c075","tid":1499433,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:19:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"995fa7ea88e38374872b7ce88b78d2af252ac58b","tid":1499433,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:21:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7baf02a627810553ac2b3ed3d1591363a580204c","tid":1499433,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0688a247f4f21377d8361dc1ef36a949a0107531","tid":1499433,"uid":15605,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:31:16.000Z","msg":"刁狗呢啲垃圾搞文革之前要睇下自己有冇老毛既斤兩，一個唔小心分分鐘革咗自己先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d836de880ec739ad7697e67e3d68bb2538937dc2","tid":1499433,"uid":197243,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:44:35.000Z","msg":"香港人一向係中国人既眼中釘"},{"pid":"ac2af851552de5592ac7a79548e8c086a2555aa5","tid":1499433,"uid":103230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:46:53.000Z","msg":"香港人咪就係佢地昔日既地主<br />\n<br />\n簡單"},{"pid":"8a3595c22eae91874a47b8f2a41d0a6c8932501b","tid":1499433,"uid":156878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:47:17.000Z","msg":"台灣, 香港, 新疆, 西藏,  福建"},{"pid":"321fb571e71256f4c3969633c08a1ecf9d70cdfc","tid":1499433,"uid":101498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:00:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">824星期六<br />\n機場 觀塘 禮賓府</div></span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v4LeZ1G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv4LeZ1G.png&h=5d800a63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">光復香港，時代革命</div></span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d90be4a6de6c2874c472b2251ac0f6043d273c0","tid":1499433,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">破而後立</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nFfam93.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnFfam93.jpg&h=f46c0dc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n'If not us, <strong>WHO</strong>? <br />\nIf not now, <strong>WHEN</strong>?'<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">RIGHT THE WRONG, FREE HONG KONG</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\"><strong><em>毋忘六烈 八百義 兩眼 三十骨折 手腳筋<br />\n過期毒氣 元朗黑夜 811警暴 雙肺 一裙 無數屈辱私刑<br />\n撤回 定性 釋士 究警 普選</em></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n試問誰還未發聲<br />\n都捨我其誰<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>衛我城</strong></span><br />\n天生有權還有心可作主<br />\n誰要認命噤聲</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qmfE8Gr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqmfE8Gr.jpg&h=24d31a61&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Be Water</div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Push HARDER than yesterday<br />\nIf you want a DIFFERENT TOMORROW</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">中國威脅論\n打壓外資 染紅企業\n清算航運龍頭大本營\n白色恐怖橫行\n貨幣操控 嚴重影響全球經濟\n反人道 暴力主義\n反人權 軍事鎮壓\n誣陷扣留外國領事館職員\n公然宣佈國際聲明已成歷史\n人面識別系統全面入侵私隱\n施壓公共交通系統公司\n施壓司法機關系統\n掌控執法部門成管治機器\n新聞媒體自由封鎖 假新聞一言定音\n不容異見之聲 網絡圍牆封鎖屏蔽 \n宣揚一人執政黨國 造王英雄主義\n改造信仰 壓抑宗教自由\n中國人納粹主義浪潮入侵西方主義國家\n新疆教育營文化滅絕非我族類\n六四屠殺事件 歷史檔案依然封鎖\n維權人士牢獄之災 每年逃亡海外\n陳秋實律師片段、多位內地藝術家遭禁聲\n強制拘留 驗血 政治檢控 勞改\n人民日報種族歧視深膚色人種\n警隊內部以&lsquo;甲甴&rsquo;爭議詞代指運動人士\n解僱 清算 追捕 人面拍攝 ID追蹤</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><div style=\"text-align: right;\">&lsquo;&lsquo;We work in the dark to serve the light.&rsquo;&rsquo;</div></span>"},{"pid":"565813811775983355cb3a90f1e059140dc63abc","tid":1499433,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:08:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d46e62c22ac370ef07d22777eb091827d5d61ec","tid":1499433,"uid":23239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T03:22:54.000Z","msg":"push!!!"}]}